data.description: SELLER IS PAYING $ 3000 TOWARDS BUYERS CLOSING COSTS!! BACK ON THE MARKET DUE TO BUYER'S LIFE EVENTS. FULL INSPECTION REPORT AVAILABLE W PROOF OF REPAIRS! This gorgeous, well-maintained home located in the executive Wren Creek neighborhood in Blythewood has it all and is move in ready! 4 bedrooms, 3 1/2 baths, formal dining room, large master on main w spacious walk-in closet, double vanity, garden tub and separate shower. Upon entry, you are greeted by gleaming hardwoods that lead into the bright and airy great room with cathedral ceiling and gas fireplace. The gourmet eat-in kitchen features stainless steel appliances, gas range, wall oven, custom cabinets and granite countertops. As you head upstairs, you will find the 2nd master suite, 2 additional bedrooms, and a large bonus room w spacious walk-in closet. A screened in porch overlooks the beautiful backyard w grilling deck and storage shed. It is fully fenced and offers great usable space. Storage galore and a 3 car garage complete the picture making this the perfect home! Great location just minutes off I-77 close to Ft. Jackson and downtown Columbia!
